rlVizLib.messaging
Class AbstractMessage

java.lang.Object
  rlVizLib.messaging.AbstractMessage
Direct Known Subclasses:
AgentMessages, AgentShellMessages, EnvironmentMessages, EnvironmentShellMessages
public class AbstractMessage
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract Message is the root of the entire RLViz Messaging System. All of the subclasses for agents, environments, agentShell, environmentShell extend Abstract Message. Abstract message using the strategy design pattern to wrap up a GenericMessage.

Author:
Brian Tanner
